error.[t]error_noplaydata_text:
To join Buckler's Boot Camp and use content linked to play data, you must have STREET FIGHTER 6 play data.

If you have played STREET FIGHTER 6, please verify the following:
- You have played online
- You have linked a logged in CAPCOM ID to a platform account used to play STREET FIGHTER 6

For users who have played STREET FIGHTER 6 offline or have not played at all, we have prepared content that you can enjoy even if you don't register.
